            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Dado que las expresiones se convierten en valores, podemos almacenar los resultados de los cálculos en variables.</p><p>Almacena el resultado del cálculo en la variable <code>total</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" privatePosts = \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" publicPosts = \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" total = privatePosts + publicPosts\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Total posts:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(total)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"46\" endIndex=\"51\" /><option startIndex=\"52\" endIndex=\"53\" /><option startIndex=\"54\" endIndex=\"80\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Total posts:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"13\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>total</code> seguido de <code>=</code> y finalmente <code>privatePosts + publicPosts</code>.</p></body></html>"
